{"tid":1673184,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我希望大家可以有共識 絕對唔會用暴力影響區選","createTime":"2019-10-24T13:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T18:13:47.000Z","uid":9394,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c3bcffe4c2ab2ef026b2ee629b98832288b39aad","tid":1673184,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"雖然我諗手足無咁蠢 但都想大家有強烈共識講明唔會搞區選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包括保皇黨既office/banner/人<br />\n唔希望可以比到機會林鄭cancal區選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n破壞行為亦唔會係我地手做<br />\n雖然血債票償係好On9 <br />\n但無可否認區選係制度內好重要既一環 <br />\n贏左就可以令民建聯班仆街cut曬budget <br />\n亦有大量手足去左參選 花左好多心機<br />\n一齊漂漂亮亮咁贏呢一仗 好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bff760c28175d14cbd65c073a060bb33302f8f7","tid":1673184,"uid":98700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n[國際戰線] 香港抗爭動作遊戲(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望各位多多支持</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1e9eb778c0c626d05776852657d89f038f6918a5","tid":1673184,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Squwor1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquwor1.gif&h=dc4a280e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=89c31693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5c6cbc73b4daed571100bf69dad528a8fdc30d5a","tid":1673184,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"畫面撚你話事咩屌<img sr